  <brief_title>Needlescopic-assisted Uniportal vs Uniportal VATS</brief_title>
  <acronym>UNeed Trail</acronym>
  <official_title>Needlescopic-assisted Uniportal VATS Versus Conventional Uniportal VATS. A Randomized Prospective Noninferiority Study</official_title>
