  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' study aims is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of uniportal VATS under
      assistance of needlescopic instruments through additional 2-3 mm ports compared to
      conventional uniportal VATS in patients with lung lesions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
